[%@library directory_options]
[para]
[:en] The [`enum class] type [`directory_options] is a bitmask type
([#bitmask.types]) that specifies bitmask constants used to identify directory
traversal options, with the meanings listed in Table
[#tab:fs.enum.directory_options].
[:zh_CN] [`enum class] 类型 [`directory_options] 是一种位掩码类型
（[#bitmask.types]），指定了一组用于标定目录遍历选项的位掩码常量，其含义在表
[#tab:fs.enum.directory_options] 中列出。

